<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idca95f916-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s2811"><num value="2811">§ 2811.</num><heading> Private sector</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Committee and each covered agency may, to the maximum extent practical, rely upon and use the private sector in the United States for the provision of geospatial data and services.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idca95f917-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">(<ref href="/us/pl/115/254/dB/tVII/s759C">Pub. L. 115–254, div. B, title VII, § 759C</ref>, <date date="2018-10-05">Oct. 5, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/3427">132 Stat. 3427</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
